  <h1>Objects</h1>
  <p>
  In this section of the <a href="create-service">New Service</a> form, you can configure the content of the service menu on the <a href="../../../search/persons/person">My Trust Assets</a> and <a href="../../../objects/object/related-tickets">Related requests</a> pages.
  </p>
  <p>Options:</p>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>Display on objects of the following type</strong> - successively select the object types on whose pages you want to show the edited service in the service menu to create a new request. Enter part of the object type name in the field and then select the appropriate type from the drop-down menu. This will add the selected type to the list below the input field.</li>
  </ul>

</asp:Content>
